Revision history for Gtk2-Notify

0.05    Wed, 12 Nov 2008 07:47:10 +0100
        * Port build system to Module::Install.

0.04    Thu, 04 Oct 2007 14:26:02 +0200
        * Let set_hint() stringify it's argument when it doesn't know
          what to do with it.
        * Don't compile things with -Werror.
        * Be more portable by using ppport.h.
        * Several minor, not user-visible improvements.

0.03    Thu, 31 May 2007 13:48:03 +0200
        * Bind status icon functions.
        * Various improvements.

0.02    Mon, 28 Aug 2006 13:07:56 +0200
        * Make the last three arguments to ->new optional.
        * Make the last two arguments to ->update optional.
        * Make the userdata in add_action optional.
        * Also initialize Gtk2 when called with -init.
        * Port the pynotify examples.

0.01    Sun, 27 Aug 2006 17:52:24 +0200
        * First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
